2736,9,C009_P1_pdf.txt,326,"Open Access This article is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution-  NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International License, which permits any  non-commercial use, sharing, distribution and reproduction in any medium or  format, as long as you give appropriate credit to the original author(s) and the source, provide  a link to the Creative Commons licence, and indicate if you modified the licensed material."
2737,9,C009_P1_pdf.txt,327,You do not have permission under this licence to share adapted material derived from this  article or parts of it.
