5548,20,C020_P1_pdf.txt,1,"Keywords: LLM;Textcategorization;Contentanalysis;Qualitativecoding;Digital humanities 1 Introduction Textcategorization,commonlyreferredtoascontentanalysisandqualitativecodinginthe social sciences, plays an important role in scholarly research and industrial applications."
