6740,25,C025_P1.txt,60,"The judge evaluates the PDF only, not the underlying code or data."
6741,25,C025_P1.txt,61,Rankings should not be taken at face value.
6742,25,C025_P1.txt,62,"That's why everything is  open source  — code, data, and papers are all public so anyone can spot errors, report issues, and contribute improvements."
