7361,28,C028_P1_pdf.txt,248,"Original Script linterp <- function (x , y ) { a <- coef ( lm ( y ~ x ) ) [2] x . min <- x [1]; x . max <- x [ length ( x ) ] y . out <- numeric ( length ( x ) ) # ... rest of computation ... return ( y . out ) } Injected Error linterp <- function (x , y , x . out ) { stop ( "" Not implemented "" ) } B Prompt Examples for Prompt-based Repair Below are the templates for the prompts used for the three different context levels in the prompt-based repair workflow."
7362,28,C028_P1_pdf.txt,249,These prompts were programmatically filled and instantiated with the respective synthetic samples.
