8362,32,C032_P1_pdf.txt,141,"Generated Idea.As discussed in Section 3,Th e A I Sc i e n t i s tfirst generates an idea based on the provided template and its previous archive of discoveries."
8363,32,C032_P1_pdf.txt,142,"The idea in the selected paper was proposed in the 6th iteration of the algorithm and aims to improve the ability of diffusion models to capture both global structure and local details in a 2D dataset, by proposing two branches in the standard denoiser network."
8364,32,C032_P1_pdf.txt,143,"This is a well-motivated direction that has been the primary reason for researchers adopting diffusion models over prior styles of generative models such as VAEs (Kingma 7 The AI Scientist: Towards Fully Automated Open-Ended Scientific Discovery and Welling, 2014) and GANs (Goodfellow et al., 2014), and to the best of our knowledge has not been widely studied."
