9846,36,C036_P1_pdf.txt,257,"In Proceedings of the 2022 ACM Conference on Fairness, Accountability, and Transparency . 789–798. [22] Luke Hewitt, Ashwini Ashokkumar, Isaias Ghezae, and Robb Willer. 2024."
