9848,36,C036_S1_pdf.txt,0,"Journal of Further and Higher Education ISSN: 0309-877X (Print) 1469-9486 (Online) Journal homepage: www.tandfonline.com/journals/cjfh20 Use of artiﬁcial intelligence tools by doctoral students: a mixed-methods explanatory- sequential investigation Muhammad Naveed Akbar To cite this article: Muhammad Naveed Akbar (2025) Use of artiﬁcial intelligence tools by doctoral students: a mixed-methods explanatory-sequential investigation, Journal of Further and Higher Education, 49:7, 995-1013, DOI: 10.1080/0309877X.2025.2515135 To link to this article: https://doi.org/10.1080/0309877X.2025.2515135 © 2025 The Author(s)."
