10013,36,C036_S1_pdf.txt,165,So it helped me to revise and change my language.
10014,36,C036_S1_pdf.txt,166,"And sometimes, you know, the  word limits may be like 200 words, and I write 500 and I like let ChatGPT help me to shorten  my passage."
10015,36,C036_S1_pdf.txt,167,"(Teng, lines 553–557) I still think chat GPT for now can only do some simple or baby step work, but for like reading  articles, synthesize and summarize tons of tons of references."
